{"tid":1983602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"酒吧延長停業14日 業界促政府提供15萬資助交租","createTime":"2020-04-22T02:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T11:42:28.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c0af60f9d1d2cbabd16251fb13032b9ab25c64","tid":1983602,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥今日宣布延長限聚令及規管食肆等防疫措施14日。香港酒吧業協會表示不滿，要求政府向業界作出更多賠償，並推出第三輪抗疫基金提供一筆過15萬資助讓業界交租。<br />\n<br />\n協會副主席錢雋永於上周五（17日）約見食物及衛生局副局長徐德義反映業界意見，並遞交請願信。酒吧業協會認為停業令導致全港酒吧停工接近一個月，加上政府第二輪防疫基金仍未開始接受申請，導致酒吧資金流停頓，員工被迫放無薪假。錢雋永在會上要求政府如再延長有關停業令必須為酒吧業作出更多賠償，幫助業界紓困。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1251988/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD14%E6%97%A5-%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E4%BF%83%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B15%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E4%BA%A4%E7%A7%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1251988%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%2590%25A7%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25A5%25AD14%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2595%258C%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B15%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25A7%259F&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8m9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=5bd0a93c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1251988%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%2590%25A7%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25A5%25AD14%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2595%258C%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B15%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25A7%259F&h=f766ae37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht